# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:12
translate chinese izzy13_8ca62be9:

    # gl "Hey Twig! Guess what? I got the job!"
    gl "嘿，特威格！猜猜怎么着？我拿到工作了！"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:13
translate chinese izzy13_68c72b69:

    # pc "Hey, congratulations!"
    pc "嘿，恭喜！"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:14
translate chinese izzy13_5a2b96eb:

    # pc "I guess that means you'll be leaving soon, Mari?"
    pc "那是不是意味着你要很快离开了，玛丽？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:15
translate chinese izzy13_d83a5365:

    # fr "Yeah, I'm going to train her for a little while, then I'm done."
    fr "是啊，我再带她训练一阵子，然后我就退下来了。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:16
translate chinese izzy13_1591b993:

    # fr "It's a little sad, but I'm glad that Jackson has a good person to take my position."
    fr "虽然有点伤感，但我很高兴杰克逊能找到一个好人来接替我的位置。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:17
translate chinese izzy13_93f32351:

    # gl "Thanks, girl. I appreciate that."
    gl "谢谢你，姑娘。我很感激。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:18
translate chinese izzy13_0ce62e11:

    # gl "Well, let's get your order in."
    gl "那，我们来点餐吧。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:21
translate chinese izzy13_5e8dd55b:

    # "Izzy leads me back to my booth, with Mari trailing along behind her, supervising."
    "伊兹带我回到卡座，玛丽跟在她身后，在一旁监督。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:22
translate chinese izzy13_44f9ac2a:

    # gl "So what are you having today?"
    gl "今天想吃点什么？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:23
translate chinese izzy13_6c37c9c9:

    # pc "Cheeseburger with everything, fries, and a coke."
    pc "全配芝士汉堡、薯条和可乐。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:24
translate chinese izzy13_61e49ea3:

    # gl "Simple. I like it. Give me a few minutes."
    gl "简单点。我喜欢这样。等几分钟就好。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:27
translate chinese izzy13_12885faf:

    # "Izzy rushes off to the back to put my order in."
    "伊兹匆匆跑去后厨下单。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:28
translate chinese izzy13_c78badbd:

    # pc "So how are things going? How is she doing?"
    pc "最近怎么样？她适应得如何？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:29
translate chinese izzy13_85b43910:

    # fr "She's doing great so far. Jackson likes her a lot."
    fr "目前表现很棒。杰克逊特别喜欢她。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:30
translate chinese izzy13_278c283a:

    # fr "She's pretty sassy. Jackson loves that."
    fr "她挺伶俐的。杰克逊就喜欢这点。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:31
translate chinese izzy13_c478ef3e:

    # pc "Good. I'm really happy it's working out."
    pc "太好了。真高兴一切进展顺利。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:32
translate chinese izzy13_ecc2451e:

    # fr "Me too!"
    fr "我也是！"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:33
translate chinese izzy13_a3a72879:

    # fr "Well, I better get back to helping her. I'll talk to you later, [pcname]."
    fr "嗯，我得回去帮她了。待会儿再聊，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:34
translate chinese izzy13_53fa2ef6:

    # pc "Okay, see ya."
    pc "好的，回头见。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:37
translate chinese izzy13_69b02f38:

    # "Mari leaves and I play on my phone for a few minutes until Izzy returns with my food."
    "玛丽走了，我玩了几分钟手机，直到伊兹带着我的食物回来。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:40
translate chinese izzy13_3cd8bfcc:

    # gl "Got your burger ready, Twig. Enjoy."
    gl "汉堡做好了，Twig。请慢用。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:41
translate chinese izzy13_97e892af:

    # pc "Thanks! I'm sure I will."
    pc "谢谢！我肯定会吃得很开心的。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:42
translate chinese izzy13_8dc0436a:

    # gl "So you and Mari have a thing going on?"
    gl "所以你和玛丽有那么回事？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:43
translate chinese izzy13_999c143d:

    # pc "Yeah, we've been dating some."
    pc "是啊，我们约会过几次。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:44
translate chinese izzy13_f21ed68a:

    # gl "Man, she's so hot."
    gl "天啊，她真性感。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:45
translate chinese izzy13_a996b478:

    # gl "We should all three get together sometime, you know?"
    gl "咱们三个找个时间聚聚吧，你觉得呢？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:46
translate chinese izzy13_f945ea47:

    # pc "Yeah maybe. We'll see."
    pc "嗯，也许吧。到时候再说。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:47
translate chinese izzy13_0827ec33:

    # gl "Anyway, let me know if you need anything. I gotta go take care of those assholes over there."
    gl "总之，有事叫我一声。我得去应付那边那群混蛋了。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:48
translate chinese izzy13_49912e7a:

    # pc "Alright, I will."
    pc "行，我会的。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:51
translate chinese izzy13_410fc4ec:

    # "Izzy goes to help other customers and I eat my meal."
    "伊兹去招呼其他客人，我则开始吃东西。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:54
translate chinese izzy13_1afb6a34:

    # "Then a few minutes later, Izzy and Mari return."
    "几分钟后，伊兹和玛丽回来了。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:55
translate chinese izzy13_b99c5a01:

    # gl "Did you like your burger?"
    gl "汉堡好吃吗？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:56
translate chinese izzy13_a248948f:

    # pc "Of course."
    pc "当然。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:57
translate chinese izzy13_d2f1177a:

    # gl "I know, right? They're so fucking good."
    gl "对吧？那玩意儿简直太他妈好吃了。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:58
translate chinese izzy13_4a0f9f0f:

    # gl "I'm going to end up eating so many, working here. My ass is gonna get {i}fat{/i}!"
    gl "在这儿工作，我迟早要吃太多，屁股都要{i}变胖{/i}了！"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:59
translate chinese izzy13_bad98252:

    # gl "How do you stay so fit, Mari?"
    gl "玛丽，你是怎么保持这么苗条的？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:60
translate chinese izzy13_2202a21b:

    # fr "Benefits of being vegetarian."
    fr "吃素的好处。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:61
translate chinese izzy13_03e1f782:

    # gl "Well I sure as hell ain't doing that!"
    gl "那我可绝对不干那事儿！"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:62
translate chinese izzy13_481c466b:

    # gl "Anyways, have a good day, Twig. I'll see you later."
    gl "不管怎样，特维格，祝你今天过得愉快。待会儿见。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:63
translate chinese izzy13_1af352a6:

    # fr "Yeah, bye [pcname]. Thanks for coming in."
    fr "嗯，再见[pcname]。谢谢光临。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:66
translate chinese izzy13_afdbb1fc:

    # "They start to walk away, and Izzy looks back at me."
    "她们开始走开，伊齐回头看了我一眼。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:67
translate chinese izzy13_65d07413:

    # gl "You better give me a good tip. I was downright fucking pleasant."
    gl "你最好给我多给点小费。我今天可真是他妈的亲切。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:68
translate chinese izzy13_8a5abc7f:

    # pc "I'll give you more than the tip."
    pc "我会给你比小费更多的。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:69
translate chinese izzy13_8f001d5e:

    # gl "Don't tease me, Twig. I have to work 'til closing today."
    gl "别逗我，特维格。我今天要工作到打烊。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:70
translate chinese izzy13_864b9473:

    # pc "Have fun."
    pc "玩得开心。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:71
translate chinese izzy13_4772f020:

    # gl "Yeah, yeah. See ya."
    gl "嗯，嗯。再见。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:74
translate chinese izzy13_2cf41d4f:

    # "With a smile, I leave a generous tip on the table and leave."
    "我笑着在桌上留下了一笔丰厚的小费，然后离开了。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:75
translate chinese izzy13_b9414cfd:

    # "It's good to see Izzy doing well. I hope the job works out for her."
    "看到伊兹过得不错真好。希望这份工作能对她有帮助。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:1
    old "You'll need to progress far enough with Izzy that she is looking for a job. You will also have to progress far enough with Mari that she tells you she is leaving Jackson Burger."
    new "你需要和伊兹的关系进展到她正在找工作的程度。同时，你还需要和玛丽的关系进展到她告诉你她要离开杰克逊汉堡的程度。"

    # game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:2
    old "Have conversations with Izzy asking what kind of job she is looking for, then have the conversation to suggest Jackson Burger. Then this scene will happen when you next go to Jackson Burger."
    new "和伊兹聊聊她想找什么样的工作，然后建议她去杰克逊汉堡。下次你去杰克逊汉堡时，就会触发这个场景。"

